Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.07,0:02:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,780)\fad(1321,1000)\3a&00&\3c&0000A0&}狂野的森林之王
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.92,0:00:46.02,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}子供の頃の夢は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.18,0:00:49.25,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}色褪せない落書きで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.46,0:00:53.07,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}思うまま書き滑らせて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.07,0:00:58.04,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}描く未来へとつながる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.30,0:01:06.61,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}澄み渡る空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.24,0:01:10.12,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}果てしないほど青く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.19,0:01:14.14,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無邪気な心に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.36,0:01:17.74,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}充たされ魅かれてく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.90,0:01:21.70,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}やがて自由に飛びまわれる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.70,0:01:24.74,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}翼を手に入れて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.27,0:01:29.24,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無垢な瞳は求めてく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.24,0:01:33.04,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}空の向こうへ　行きたいな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.04,0:01:36.14,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}止め処ない願いから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.32,0:01:39.49,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一つだけ叶うのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.59,0:01:43.23,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}誰にも譲りたくはない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.30,0:01:47.23,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}夢を掴みたいと思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.24,0:01:50.44,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}子供の頃の夢は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.68,0:01:53.71,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}色褪せない落書きで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:57.64,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}いつまでも描き続けられた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.64,0:02:02.74,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}願う未来へとつながる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.92,0:00:46.02,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孩童時的那個夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.18,0:00:49.25,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是永不退色的塗鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.46,0:00:53.07,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}隨心所欲地去描繪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.07,0:00:58.04,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}走向自己描繪的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.30,0:01:06.61,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}萬里無雲的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.24,0:01:10.12,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無邊無際的蔚藍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.19,0:01:14.14,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}純潔無瑕的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.36,0:01:17.74,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}充盈著無限魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.90,0:01:21.70,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終於能自由翱翔於天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.70,0:01:24.74,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}長出了美麗的羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.27,0:01:29.24,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無瑕的瞳孔在尋求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.24,0:01:33.04,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}想去那天空的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.04,0:01:36.14,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}在那無數的願望中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.32,0:01:39.49,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}若是只有一個能實現
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.59,0:01:43.23,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我不願讓給任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.30,0:01:47.23,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}要緊緊抓住那夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.24,0:01:50.44,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孩童時的那個夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.68,0:01:53.71,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是永不退色的塗鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:57.64,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}永不停息地去描寫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.64,0:02:02.74,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}走向自己祈願的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.53,0:23:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,780)\fad(1321,8)\3a&00&\3c&0000A0&}紫琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.08,0:21:44.53,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}炎さえも凍てついた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:51.19,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孤独の中求む
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.19,0:21:59.85,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}魂から結びつき
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.07,0:22:07.88,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}私を恋い暖めて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.03,0:22:16.70,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嗚呼　祈りの言葉がふるえ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.04,0:22:24.41,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嗚呼　弱きいのちが消えても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.12,0:22:32.28,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}くりかえす　輪廻の流れ辿り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.39,0:22:40.90,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終わらない世界の宿命を見つめてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.96,0:22:48.40,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}くりかえし　詠われる者達よ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.41,0:22:56.54,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}守られてまどろむ宵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.08,0:21:44.53,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}就算火焰都凍結
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:51.19,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}也在孤獨中尋求
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.19,0:21:59.85,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}請用靈魂連結我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.07,0:22:07.88,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}請用愛戀溫暖我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.03,0:22:16.70,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嗚呼 那顫抖的祈願之聲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.04,0:22:24.41,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嗚呼 那脆弱的生命消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.12,0:22:32.28,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}追溯那不斷交替的輪迴之流
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.39,0:22:40.90,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}凝望那永不終結的世界的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.96,0:22:48.40,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不斷輪迴的 那些傳頌之物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.41,0:22:56.54,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}被守護著安眠的夜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.05,0:02:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起修復
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新做一個的話會快得多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.37,0:02:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是有人蓄意的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.21,0:02:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是早點回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.27,0:02:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每每想到「主」不知何時會出現就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.67,0:02:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 你們都是來幹什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.47,0:02:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不覺得可怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.39,0:02:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽了赫塔部落的事之後…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.15,0:02:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「主」大人在天亮的時候是沉睡著的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夜行的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.46,0:03:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了沒 用不著這樣擔驚受怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.09,0:03:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要別像剛才那樣發出太大的聲音的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.09,0:03:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 身體真的沒問題了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥你還是早點回去的好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.70,0:03:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷口還在疼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 身體已經沒有問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這倒是沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.11,0:03:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要幫點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.21,0:03:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那麼拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.32,0:03:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命之宿的大神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.13,0:03:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將願望寄宿於此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:04:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能讓「主」息怒就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.98,0:04:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露 剛才的言語是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.51,0:04:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對森林之神感謝的祈禱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.69,0:04:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.77,0:04:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森林給予我們食物以及草藥等恩惠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.21,0:04:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.63,0:04:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而卻觸怒了森林的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.00,0:04:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.63,0:04:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.45,0:04:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你們啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.37,0:04:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽都快下山了 快回家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.90,0:04:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好關緊門窗 安靜一些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村長 辛苦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.50,0:04:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡沒出現什麼異常吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.73,0:04:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.53,0:04:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老婆 我肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙稍微有點危機感好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.57,0:05:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也早點回家 讓家人放下心來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.35,0:05:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼小哥 艾露露他們就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候有個男人要可靠多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.63,0:05:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露也要好好聽小哥的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.77,0:05:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.45,0:05:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 阿露露
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.98,0:05:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不能好好打個招呼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.56,0:05:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是被她討厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.71,0:05:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的這麼認為嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.24,0:05:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要介意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.75,0:06:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.90,0:06:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 在這裡不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.24,0:06:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 你也會被殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.78,0:06:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.69,0:06:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 你去了打算怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森林的主人不是我們所能匹敵的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.08,0:06:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此我也不能見死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.31,0:06:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不可以讓犧牲白白增加 請你要明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶 為什麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已認真修復好神碑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.07,0:06:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我還只有阿露露那麼大的時候 姐姐她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了照顧「主」而進入了森林
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.29,0:06:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.67,0:06:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:07:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐她擁有巫女的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.68,0:07:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托姐姐的福 至今都平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的 靜悄悄地呆在這裡就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽不到聲音了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是去確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快站住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.02,0:08:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.20,0:08:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.99,0:08:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 你快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.98,0:08:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.30,0:08:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑 艾露露
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.26,0:08:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 為什麼不過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.48,0:08:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.73,0:09:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了 那傢伙走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.05,0:09:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.37,0:09:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所幸我們都平安無事…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.87,0:09:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 奇利克裡家的人也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.58,0:09:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老婆和孩子都被吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都還只是孩童
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們到底該怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.71,0:09:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.76,0:09:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.55,0:09:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是「主」的毛髮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.59,0:10:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙之所以會離開並不是因為什麼心情問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.80,0:10:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是因為討厭沾到水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.24,0:10:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥挺厲害的嘛 沒白冒這趟險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.92,0:10:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣也不能那麼亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請絕對不要再那麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.17,0:10:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.99,0:10:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼打算
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.82,0:10:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.29,0:10:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把「主」…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.21,0:10:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經有辦法了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.61,0:10:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 大家不齊心協力的話還是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.78,0:10:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們把「主」…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.98,0:10:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說它是森林的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.28,0:10:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們也不能這樣一直畏懼下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.87,0:10:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是不能這樣下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.07,0:10:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.25,0:10:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.75,0:11:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.18,0:11:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我來作誘餌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己來作誘餌 為什麼要說那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.91,0:11:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這只有身為外人的我才適合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.71,0:11:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在說這個 為什麼要由你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.96,0:11:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為就算我死去 也不會有人為此悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.29,0:11:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.05,0:11:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是說過 我們是你的家人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.03,0:11:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想讓自己的家人遇到危險
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.47,0:11:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.78,0:11:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我也不是去白白送死的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.69,0:11:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.57,0:11:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你還是我的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.63,0:11:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就一定會回到你身邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.12,0:12:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製作陷阱的話 我覺得可以利用這片池沼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.75,0:12:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後把那裡塞住變得看不出來就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.23,0:12:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當「主」追來的時候就斬斷機關的繩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 我自會逃的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.87,0:12:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是把森林之主消滅的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.02,0:12:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 會遭報應的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道就這樣眼睜睜地看著它填飽肚子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備每個晚上擔驚受怕地度過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也沒錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.02,0:12:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子這樣下去被吃掉可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.90,0:12:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.15,0:12:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我們的雙手…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥 請繼續說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.58,0:12:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「主」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露真是溫柔的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我們也不可以放棄生存
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.39,0:12:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.87,0:12:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機關也已經佈置好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來切斷繩子好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家就回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 不回去的話很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你一個的話肯定也很心虛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.40,0:13:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是出了萬一 還是人多好辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.73,0:13:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.41,0:13:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把危險的事情全推給那個小哥總不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.35,0:13:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.35,0:13:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡開始 我一個人就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這麼說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.94,0:13:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓傷員一個人過去 我就不配作男人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鐵奧羅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稱呼我名字有點不好意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.29,0:13:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都稱呼我老爺子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.46,0:13:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以小哥也喊我老爺子好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.86,0:13:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒到那個年齡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.69,0:13:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這說明大家多麼信賴我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.92,0:13:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說這話也不是該自己說的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.17,0:14:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.22,0:14:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.02,0:14:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你要為我們做那麼多的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於失去記憶的我來說 這裡就是我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.00,0:14:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥已經是我們這裡的出色的男人了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.13,0:14:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能得到你這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.59,0:14:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣 真見外
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開心的時候就應該說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.92,0:14:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.82,0:14:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.86,0:14:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.80,0:14:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣 那傢伙的身體龐大不便於行動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙上哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.06,0:15:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像護身符一樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.27,0:15:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請帶上它去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.03,0:15:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太堅硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爺子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.11,0:15:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.65,0:16:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音迫近了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.28,0:16:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.88,0:16:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥 老爺子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.89,0:16:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就現在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.51,0:16:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好勒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.32,0:16:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.08,0:16:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.58,0:16:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「主」大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來 親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.29,0:17:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.76,0:17:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它救了我一命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.77,0:17:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.99,0:17:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.14,0:17:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.78,0:17:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.11,0:17:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.83,0:17:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.37,0:18:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊沒找到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊也沒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.70,0:18:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 哪兒都找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.84,0:18:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.84,0:18:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「主」已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.49,0:18:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒危險
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.14,0:18:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.88,0:18:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.76,0:18:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.18,0:18:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候你究竟在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.48,0:18:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露你藏了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.21,0:18:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶寶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.44,0:18:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露的寶寶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.43,0:18:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.43,0:18:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.90,0:18:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這個可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露 究竟藏了些什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.58,0:18:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露的寶寶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.37,0:18:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.83,0:18:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個毛色
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個不就是「主」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.39,0:18:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「主」的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.99,0:18:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 為什麼要把那種東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露 發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.61,0:19:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我做了約定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.85,0:19:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約定？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.53,0:19:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了一件麻煩事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.56,0:19:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說怎麼辦 這樣的幼仔在親人死後活不下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.49,0:19:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但萬一活下來的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.33,0:19:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙將來也會襲擊人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.98,0:19:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不想再無謂殺生了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.50,0:19:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛降臨的生命本是純潔之物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個孩子是無罪的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.51,0:19:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為「主」大人送行的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.15,0:19:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們人類只能這樣為其送上祈禱罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.14,0:20:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.54,0:20:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.98,0:20:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.10,0:20:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.82,0:20:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 那孩子說了些莫名其妙的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.56,0:20:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.70,0:20:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得…很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.65,0:20:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.96,0:20:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開心的時候就要說出來
